<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl pb-6">
    <div class="mb-8 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-700">
        <span class="align-middle text-xl text-violet-400">#</span> About me
    </div>
    <div class="my-8 text-lg text-gray-900">
        Young <b>IT enthusiast</b>, I've been tinkering computers since I'm 12.
        <br /><br />
        Driven by my endless curiousity, it quickly evolved into a deep passion that
        spans across <b>software development 💻</b>, <b>custom PC builds 🔧</b>, <b
            >self-hosting servers 📡</b
        >,
        <b>networking 🌐</b>, <b>data privacy 👤</b> and <b
            >computer security 🔒</b
        >.
        <br /><br />
        Whether I'm writing clean, efficient code, building high-performance machines
        from the ground up, or managing my own server infrastructure, I approach
        every challenge with enthusiasm and a relentless drive to <b
            >innovate 🧠</b
        >.
        <br /><br />
        <span class="text-2xl font-semibold">
            Let's create something amazing <span
                class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 from-20% via-emerald-500 via-60% to-amber-500 to-90% bg-clip-text pb-8 pt-2 text-transparent"
                >together</span>! 🚀
            </span>
    </div>
</section>
